This paper focuses on modeling the formation of data dissemination in online social networks, which involves multiple interrelated factors such as users' social relationships, users' interests, and content semantics. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
